  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817390/extras/d802b74bee3c297f773ed068ce502860.avif?t=1772418861\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shino has been the protagonist's childhood friend since they were kids.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She loves gaming, is skilled at cooking, has a great personality, is busty, and has a cute face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She is like a symbol of a man's \"preferences\"...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl with such high specs that anyone would take a second glance if they passed her by.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, everyday life with her doesn't seem to be just peaceful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817390/extras/0717ea52f2afded3a0c8128d293891f1.avif?t=1772418861\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This work is an exploration RPG without combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the first half, you have 10 days of free attendance before the summer vacation, with 50 turns in total including morning, noon, evening, night, and late night, freely exploring the city of Suō where the heroine lives and spending ordinary days while collecting flags for route branching.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the route is confirmed in the latter half, the scene falls deeper. (There is a pure love route)  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817390/extras/17b18d81278daccd6bcb574a15eab378.avif?t=1772418861\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NTR and pure love</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >66 scenes + α　10 ENDs</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817390/extras/d802b74bee3c297f773ed068ce502860.avif?t=1772418861\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shino has been the protagonist's childhood friend since they were kids.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She loves gaming, is skilled at cooking, has a great personality, is busty, and has a cute face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She is like a symbol of a man's \"preferences\"...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A girl with such high specs that anyone would take a second glance if they passed her by.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, everyday life with her doesn't seem to be just peaceful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817390/extras/0717ea52f2afded3a0c8128d293891f1.avif?t=1772418861\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This work is an exploration RPG without combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the first half, you have 10 days of free attendance before the summer vacation, with 50 turns in total including morning, noon, evening, night, and late night, freely exploring the city of Suō where the heroine lives and spending ordinary days while collecting flags for route branching.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the route is confirmed in the latter half, the scene falls deeper. (There is a pure love route)  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2817390/extras/17b18d81278daccd6bcb574a15eab378.avif?t=1772418861\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NTR and pure love</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >66 scenes + α　10 ENDs</p></li></ul>",
